    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237650/extras/d9a065bf01bb8be010229f2e2cd20705.avif?t=1747409130\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237650/extras_big/d9a065bf01bb8be010229f2e2cd20705.avif?t=1747409130 width=800 height=112 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237650/extras/f8ada1befca200277ebb3772239ffe6f.avif?t=1747409130\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237650/extras_big/f8ada1befca200277ebb3772239ffe6f.avif?t=1747409130 width=800 height=112 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Get a taste of the <i>Nightmare Busters Rebirth</i> Experience!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dive into the Kingdom of Dreams and discover the remastered and reimagined version of <i>Nightmare Busters</i>, the canceled Super Nintendo run'n gun.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Journey through the Forest, take down the nightmares in your path, and leap from branch to branch! Will you be able to defeat the mini-boss duo, Goblinly &amp; Hootley?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience modernized gameplay with a secondary weapon and three superpowers to use wisely! Master arena battles, chain your moves for the highest combo, uncover hidden secrets, and aim for the coveted S++ rank!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Warning: the game is still in development—some details may change in the final version!</strong></p>",
